    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You create a wave of energy that ripples through the earth. Terrestrial creatures in the affected area must attempt a Reflex save to avoid stumbling as the shockwave shakes the ground.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.<br><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} until the start of its next turn.<br><strong>Failure</strong> The creature falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone}.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, plus the creature takes 1d6 damage.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The area increases by 5 feet (to a 20-foot cone at 2nd level, and so on).&nbsp;</p>",
